name: THE BLUES IN MOTION
description: The Blues was created out of the blue, a random idea, for a random photoshoot and when I put these colors together they made me realize, how I was painting with my gut because later that day it was all blue , but that feeling passed. And now every time I look at this piece, It brings me peace. The Blues doesn't have to be a sad feeling, let is pass like water flowing on the sea shore.
